{"type": "article", "id": 50913, "title": "芭比推出 14 款新造型，以及，这是 Phoebe Philo 的 Céline“遗作” | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-03-08T04:04:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1580, "name": "巴黎时装周"}, {"id": 16038, "name": "BAPE"}, {"id": 934, "name": "芭比"}, {"id": 9436, "name": "Phoebe Philo"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180308120158TnJUpM9C6mdBie7h.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/new-look-proposes-layoffs-and-store-closures\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>英国快时尚品牌 New Look 将关闭 60 家门店，裁员千人</strong></a> | 据路透社报道，由于业绩持续下滑，New Look 将关闭英国 593 家门店中的 60 家，同时目前 15300 名员工中可能将有 980 人因此离职。最新财报显示，本财年前三季度，New Look 营收已同比下跌 6.3% 至 10.7 亿英镑，税前利润亏损则高达 1.23 亿英镑。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/forbespr/2018/03/06/forbes-32nd-annual-worlds-billionaires-issue/#36ac0c3810e0\" rel=\"nofollow\">LVMH 集团创始人家族成为《财富》杂志排行榜时尚类首富</a></strong> | 过去一年内，LVMH 集团主席 Arnault Bernard 及其家族的财富增加了 305 亿美元，达到 720 亿美元，这使得他在财富榜上的排名上升到第 4 位，成为欧洲首富。与此同时，Zara 母公司 Inditex 集团创始人&nbsp;Amancio Ortega 从榜单的第 4 位跌至第 6 位。这也是他 2011 年以来首次跌出前五。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2018/3/undercover-end-womens-show-paris-fashion-week-mens-presentations\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本设计师品牌&nbsp;Undercover 将不再发布女装系列</a></strong> | 本季巴黎时装周上发布的 Undercover 2018 秋冬女装系列将是该品牌在 T 台上展示的最后一个女装系列。此前，该品牌只有女装走秀，男装则通过 Lookbook 发布。设计师高桥盾计划从今年 6 月起举办第一次男装秀，而女装系列则只在巴黎 Showroom 中展示。他表示设计女装系列时“很难在 T 台上兼顾创意及实穿性”，而男装则相反。另一个原因可能是，该品牌主要营收仍然来自男装。<br></p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>国际妇女节前一天，美泰（Mattel）<a href=\"https://barbie.mattel.com/en-us/about/role-models.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">在官网上公布了 14 款新芭比造型</a>。其中“Shreo（女英雄）”系列新增 11款，“Inspiring Women（励志女性）”系列新增 3 款。</p><p>两个系列均以全球知名女性为制作模板，不同之处在于“Sheroes” 2015 年已经推出，主要关注当前“红人”，此前包括穆斯林击剑选手 Ibtihaj Muhammad 、导演 Ava DuVernay、大码模特 Ashley Graham、芭蕾舞者 Misty Copeland等。“Inspiring Women（励志女性）”为今年新增，关注那些改变历史、为世界作出杰出贡献的女性。</p><p>三款“Inspiring Women”系列芭比包括：墨西哥艺术家 Frida Kahlo、美国飞行家&nbsp;Amelia Earhart 以及 NASA 科学家 Katherine Johnson。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308101439jLWmPK0zQ7E1ZTyl.png\" data-ratio=\"1.571429\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308101505hH9YJPA15VRjr4Ck.png\" data-ratio=\"1.571429\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308101514EsiU3brnC8Mvht5X.png\" data-ratio=\"1.571429\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p>今年的新“Shero”包括：《神奇女侠》导演 Patty Jenkins、韩裔美国单板滑雪选手 Chloe Kim、澳大利亚动物保护者 Bindi Irwin、英国拳击运动员&nbsp;Nicola Adams、德国服装设计师 Leyla Piedayesh、波兰记者&nbsp;Martyna Wojciechowska、意大利女足队员&nbsp;Sara Gama、法国米其林二星主厨&nbsp;Hélène Darroze。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308100938jcsmbgrUi92eI8yG.png\" data-ratio=\"1.571429\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018030810095723H7zDa0WNeMCgFG.png\" data-ratio=\"1.571429\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308101016fAiVowS67N3OLnDm.png\" data-ratio=\"1.571429\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308101033zMT16swC4JOpXq0u.png\" data-ratio=\"1.571429\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308101045NWy43sBfx2nOUCp9.png\" data-ratio=\"1.571429\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308101115oejcWvMxCmhPsJrX.png\" data-ratio=\"1.571429\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308101129N3pbDytcMFkYZgPn.png\" data-ratio=\"1.571429\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308101138AkJFR5HvWNmaTBL2.png\" data-ratio=\"1.571429\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p>另外还有三位中国女性：女排国家队成员惠若琪、旧金山芭蕾舞团首席演员谭元元和演员关晓彤。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803081011562u5SEzUfV8WDZBFp.png\" data-ratio=\"1.571429\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308101212Y13FLSR57l9VxBNU.png\" data-ratio=\"1.571429\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308101220ZLHbj74y2rzXhcfB.png\" data-ratio=\"1.571429\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/tags/bape\" rel=\"nofollow\">BAPE</a> 与日本玩具公司&nbsp;<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/tags/medicom-toy\" rel=\"nofollow\">Medicom Toy</a>&nbsp;将于 3 月 10 日发售一个新的合作胶囊系列，亮点在于粉、黄、蓝三色交织的迷彩服，以及新版本的 BE@RBRICK 积木熊。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308103347QzU6FwcCa1J8EugG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308103402eunbcmSq2krFYCPT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666867\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308103414mi9SkCuGUY8vNjHl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666867\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308103422m0U73pgQhe5KwVHo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666867\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308103448P6tzbUaYG2917A8R.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>巴黎时装周最后一天。</p><p>Céline 公布了前创意总监 Phoebe Philo 的最后一个系列——严格地说，是过渡系列。Phoebe Philo 已于去年底离职，而继任者 Hedi Slimane 2 月 1 日才上任，因此 2018 年秋冬系列由&nbsp;Phoebe Philo 带领了 10 年的工作室集体完成，被认为承载了&nbsp;Phoebe Philo 剩下的一些思考。</p><p>与往日隆重的大秀不同，这次没有模特，也没有秀场。展示会在&nbsp;Céline 位于巴黎维维恩大街的总部举行，24 套 Look 挂在衣架上，还贴有卷了边的数字标签。它们看上去仍然是经典的&nbsp;Phoebe Philo 风格：线条简洁的大码外套、阔腿裤，显眼的配饰，以及硬朗的西装。</p><p>官方未发布现场图片，只有 Lookbook。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308084215NSH7D1udnztW5aK6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308104915rZAHUtwhP5Dpxzcg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803081049230wMQfI2yDCEe7mNi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308104931ENImAoUu8sp7zZBV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308104938OL9wUpHoqAX103Tz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308104945mj1ad7eGLXSZhut5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803081049529v1WK3hGt7egqNSl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308105001PaFyhu273Tit9Jfm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308105011lvQwkx5dTmFbrRZa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308105020pi5Kx0eVk6fD3m8Q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308105028NlpQaRXs2HzVZMd0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803081051461qJsapluCRtQT5ro.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308105155KLj9DToGzgvtkQcp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308105202tcWi5MQCEe9pnGgU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308105211gLkpvANjWe3XUPDI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308105218OjA2nMDzBEVhYZSL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308105226cpJt1sZPfmRdnuwC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308105235FaOuRsZGnQKMlY5b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308105243ZO1KD0MoeiEkw9Sh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308105253ZrGmqbzLTJjkIeFU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308105305uK1Cbqix23IWmJka.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803081053163AFCp9KR0NE4Qohs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803081053255JST6DzpLUPFfa3I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308105335wTxQNmvrbiStHc0C.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2018/3/paris-fashion-week-fall-winter-2018-streetsnaps-part-2\" rel=\"nofollow\">潮流媒体 Hypebeast</a>&nbsp;和时尚博客 the Satorialist 发布了巴黎时装周期间的街拍合辑，我们选取了其中一些有趣的：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803081103533KAabt1WCugZyXBU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308110409WJHlt1aTC0wcESvL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308110420qM5wOEmBvzY1Ja8A.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308110434zWpe3FDoKrLjJqIf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308110449qZzrG8IOtDjNueJX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803081105047Yomx2WI5krJCLin.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308110515uLbfTvYemS7HQkay.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308110528Q6J2wF8dAtp7Xs0B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308110550z1ha2AoSrXctW6xf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308110607VoZFz0657jfO1kTi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308110622jQWaYHunTcp0MObh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308110643ow1KRIWSCjsp8HZ0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308111027HYIoVraqsb0g67C5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.501695\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308111110u6vs95nIgGYrpQUA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308111121PlVj86sgtu2oixB4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://fashionista.com/2018/03/best-paris-fashion-week-street-style-fall-2018\" rel=\"nofollow\">时尚媒体 Fashionista</a>&nbsp;回顾了本季巴黎时装周上的 8 个时尚趋势。看上去不太新鲜，但的确是跨品牌出现频率最高的元素。它们包括：<br></p><p><strong>1、80 年代强势女性风格（Power Women）</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308111539BOsRgH7cXjdNx3K8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Nina Ricci</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308111620RtdBe6W2uYKgihSp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Alexander McQueen</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308111632Cem4wcMFHlE1k9to.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Miu Miu</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong>2、夸张帽饰</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308111803aA8Ei74od3eLUfBR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Jacquemus</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308111828p4c6kIWYlDO79tHN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Dior</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308111853mN0dqnkehaj48SKw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Maison Margiela</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong>3、亮片及漆皮</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308111953qHdw0zAPrn5vbUtV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Balmain</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308112039G6tz5d3vUiLsY0u4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Dior</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308112121MiLQ47SRqNJIHnpf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Saint Laurent</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong>4、格纹</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308112243g4xvOLtBFT92jmf6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Carven</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308112300mEYrTNWA5fB4GXgP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Loewe</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308112329BQWzHADSGpoXC6PJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Stella McCartney</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong>5、层叠穿搭</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803081125186DjKApZa1qYm2NXs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Balenciaga</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308112536O5DPJa3Zj1HmqEux.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Chanel</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308112558U2q7u3GYDKS9IbOt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Yohji Yamamoto</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong>6、浪漫风格的连衣裙</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308112718gORZBzcqXuvtbJQK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Givenchy</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308112729zFnlEC985Qw0DZor.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Valentino</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308112740vJX3L4nTRqWU1IaQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Louis Vuitton</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong>7、夸张的披风</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308112930EdZiw6zx1XIGlOPD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Maison Margiela</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308112938btcT6vOj7MiayGRz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Stella McCartney</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308112945BGRM0HJSC8TiY4UO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Off-White</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong>8、豹纹</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308113048GJCjq9AMvQzrViE8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Balenciaga</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308113059vNkQ9sn73HqjDpyo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Givenchy</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180308113108VgAvoPx3Rm5rsiqM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Vivienne Westwood</figcaption> </figure></div><p>题图：Undercover</p>"}